summary: SummaryIf you prefer an automatic eyeliner to one you need to sharpen, open your eyes to IT Cosmetics Superhero No-Tug Retractable Eyeliner!

faceoff_positive.headline: Eyeliner

faceoff_negative.comments: I used to use the old version of this product which I loved, then they reformulated and switched from a twist to a sharpener which was awful.  I ordered multiple versions thinking I got a bad product but they were all bad. Then I found this this product and love it, but I had a hard time tracking it down because it was constantly sold out, so I ordered 3. 1 of the 3 was non useable - dry, scratchy. I'm frustrated and disappointed that my experience with what used to be my go to eyeliner has now been consistently poor products. I'm hesitant to order this product again because I don't trust that I'll receive a good product.
faceoff_negative.headline: Used to be great, not anymore
